OL,5, Sian Griffiths is desperate to get back
OL,6, to work but feels "ashamed" the "fog of
OL,7, long Covid" has kept her off for the   
OL,8, past 18 months.                        
OL,10,F"I can't drive far, I forget to close  
OL,11,Fdoors, I burn food and when I'm reading
OL,12,Fmy brain turns some words into others. 
OL,13,FI lose concentration," she said.       
OL,15,FSian is one of a record 1.3 million    
OL,16,Fpeople in the UK living with long Covid
OL,17,F- more than 2% of the population.      
OL,19,FThe only thing that lifts the cloud of 
OL,20,Flong Covid for her is wild swimming.   
